      "options": {
        "content": "### Critical service URLs\n- RouteMQ metrics: `http://app:8080/metrics` inside Docker; Prometheus host UI: `http://localhost:19090`\n- Grafana: `http://localhost:3000`\n- Streamlit operator dashboard / Model Registry: `http://localhost:8501`\n- MQTT broker: `mqtt://localhost:1883`\n\nRunbook hints: if RouteMQ is down, check the app container, `/metrics` endpoint, and Prometheus Targets page before reloading Grafana dashboards.",
